Havotron looked amazed as the doors shut, having only just sent 
Phebus to retrieve him.  "Spinister.  I know you are thinking my 
decision to allow Megaton into my ranks, but I do believe he will be 
the answer for Megatron I was looking for, and once we are done 
with him, he is nothing once again a lonely beast looking for 
something to fight with. "

Havok silently looked him over, waiting for a response.
